RESTLoader gets EVENTS and shows the list of all events. Each can be clicked and EventDetailsActivity opens...

Organizing calendar adapters, optimizing code. Added scrollView on CreateEvent

CalendarAdapter is an abstract class now and every CalendarAdapterX extends it. The abstract class offers a shared implementation of calculateViewDimension and imposes a method generateDayViews() that have to be implemented in child classes. Calendarctivities are extending Calendar Activity clss for similar reasons
Availability Calendar has restrictions now. User cant go wondering of to months that are in the event....

Parsing the new event format where each user comes with: user_email, email_invitation and availability... Also I added a new object UserAvailability iin the model package that wrapps the mentioned user availability
